===============================================================================================================================
Rewrite php scripts to use a Document class with the follwing methods:

setDocumentTag($str);
setHTMLTag($str);	# the xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" part of <html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> tag
setTitle($str);
addHeadContent($str);	# used for adding meta, link etc in the head section of a HTML document
addContent($str);	# adds content in the body
getHTML();		# retrievs the HTML source code
displayHTML();		# displays the HTML code


===============================================================================================================================
security groups: 
	groupdid -1 : all systems
	groupid > 0 : other system groups
security group user:
	security groupid, userid
security group system:
	security groupid, systemid

- There should be a location view (the current overview, detailed etc)
- There should be user defined group view
